# DOCUMENTATION IS PART OF THE DELIVERABLE

## Mandatory Files (docs/)
- docs/01_project_rules.md — coding standards, tech stack
- docs/02_database_schema.md — schema, tables, relationships
- docs/03_api_and_integrations.md — tRPC procedures, external APIs
- docs/04_features_audit.md — feature matrix with status
- docs/05_dependency_graph.md — component/utility dependencies
- docs/06_tasks.md — master checklist for fixes
- docs/engineering/SCALE_CONSIDERATIONS.md — prototype-to-production bridge
- CHANGELOG.md — Added, Changed, Fixed, Security

## Documentation Standards
- JSDoc/TSDoc on exported functions and types
- Database migrations: comment block explaining WHY
- tRPC procedures: auth requirement, input/output types

## After Every Change
- Update CHANGELOG.md under [Unreleased]
- Update docs/06_tasks.md if fixing an audit item
